<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>A class for a command line input option. </para>



<para><literallayout><computeroutput>Each option is defined by a tag (i.e., the string following a hyphen)
and a value (the next string after the tag).
</computeroutput></literallayout> </para>
